-- Insurer Catlin receives takeover approach from XL Group
-- By Esha Vaish in Bengaluru
-- Wed Dec 17, 2014 08:39AM EST
-- None



Dec 17 (Reuters) - Catlin Group Ltd <CGL.L> said it received a takeover approach from XL Group Plc <XL.N> that valued the Bermuda-based insurer at 2.53 billion pounds ($3.98 billion).

Under the indicative terms of the offer, XL would pay 410 pence in cash and 0.130 shares for each Catlin share, the London-listed company said in a statement. [ID:nRSQ0433Aa]